om/news/music/blackpink-jennie-you-and-me-3508828">宣布了她的新单曲《You &amp; Me》</a> 。</p><p>在其他地方，韩国流行女子组合<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/gi-dle">(G)I-DLE</a>的<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/song-yuqi">Yuqi</a><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/gi-dles-yuqi-doesnt-think-she-has-succeeded-yet-3508834">畅谈了成功以及她认为自己尚未实现的原因</a>。女子组合<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/newjeans">NewJeans</a>发布了 2023 年<a href="https://www.nme.com/games/league-of-legends"><em>英雄联盟</em></a>世界锦标赛新歌<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/newjeans-gods-league-of-legends-worlds-anthem-2023-3508840">《Gods》</a> 。</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/police-drop-charges-mamamoo-hwasa-indecent-performance-3508852">警方撤销对 MAMAMOO 华莎涉嫌“不雅”表演的指控的</a>帖子首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
